 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ECervalis, LLC provides information technology infrastructure solutions. The company\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s solutions include business continuity/rapid recovery, managed hosting, managed security, managed storage, networking and telecommunications, and co-location services. Its managed security solutions include firewall protection, intrusion detection, backup services, virtual private network services, multi-level virus protection, vulnerability scan, and consulting services. The company\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s options services include routers and switches, remote access, intrusion detection and protection, reboot services, network monitoring and reporting, and load balancing. Its clients include financial services, insurance, health care/pharmaceuticals, government, education, utilities, energy, media/entertainment, manufacturing, transportation, retail, and not-for-profit industries. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Shelton, Connecticut. It has data center facilities in New York and Connecticut.\u003C/p\u003E",
